    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Spoons designed to serve soup, stews, or similar dishes from a porringer, which is a small bowl or basin, typically with a handle.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
